      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an uncompromising standard, its condition is truly beyond reproach, presenting in showroom-state both aesthetically and mechanically. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this unit offers an unparalleled ownership opportunity. Every detail reflects a legacy of meticulous care, ensuring a driving experience that remains as refined as the day it first left the factory.",
