    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m absolutely heartbroken to let go of my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this beauty! It\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just left the dealership. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is it! Come give it a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
