      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_21_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_21",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 high-pressure die-cast iron block inline-six. This powerhouse utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag Type D 6-speed manual transmission and a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock. This example retains its factory-correct suspension geometry with aluminum control arms and remains free of subframe fatigue. The exterior finish and interior upholstery exhibit zero degradation, preserving the tactile feedback and mechanical purity expected of a peak-era M-division machine. All service intervals are current, with valve clearances recently shimmed to factory specifications.",
      "price": 49250.0,
