    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections; it has been treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition\u2014the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively through authorized dealerships. All original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover are included. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
